snippet.title: Erasing the Hard Drive
snippet.description:
Well, my daughter Jessica, invited me to do an interview with her about magic mushrooms as an interlude for my Nature series. I liked the idea because it is a fitting subject to augment my series, a welcome change in my posting pace, and a chance to offer some needed insight into the hallucinogenic world. Everybody wins. 

Jess and I discuss how plant hallucinogens open the mind. We talk about how psychedelics heal anxiousness by fostering love and compassion within the individual by breaking down negative thought patterns. We discuss parenting, and some personal experiences in navigating plant medicines with one's offspring.  

Jessica is an advocate for magic mushrooms, and this was a way to bring about wholesome, thoughtful awareness to a broader audience regarding a very misunderstood subject. Governments have worked very hard to keep these very powerful, natural energies out of the hands of the masses due to the threat they present to mind control. Make no mistake, billions have been spent to keep everyone overly confused, pharmacologically dumbed-down, and saturated in needless fear so as to never have a rational dialog regarding our birthright, because if you actually found out about and engaged the hallucinogenic world, you couldn’t be governed anymore.

snippet.title: Nature as Identity, part 2
snippet.description:
Today we begin a deep dive into electromagnetics in this part 2 of my series on identifying through Nature.

We all, the planet, the galaxy, the universe, are forces undergirded by electromagnetics. Electromagnetics suspend the nuclei that compose us, hold the earth in orbit, form the gravity grounding you to this planet, and spin the earth on its axis. Electromagnetism composes the Milky Way galaxy to its shape, and black holes to their magnetism. It outlines and informs the pyramids at Giza, while at the same time suspending your soul in your body. For electromagnetism is the basis of existence, the organization of form, and the bridge between aether and matter. 

With cameo appearances from Billy Carson, Dr. Rupert Sheldrake, and Joseph Campbell, and music from none other than Elvis, this video will render electromagnetics and alchemical symbolism to you so vividly, you will find yourself falling in love with yourself/Nature/God without even having to try. That, at least, is my hope. 

This makes me think of the line from Shawshank Redemption when Andy wrote in his farewell letter, "Remember Red...Hope, is a good thing, maybe the best of things, and no good thing ever dies."

Much love to all. 
Chuck

snippet.title: Dethroning the Psychopaths
snippet.description:
I have chosen the vein of Christianity to open a dialog regarding the ruling agencies who have controlled humanity since inception. 

Michael Tsarion begins and concludes our dialogue today because he always answers questions using history and philosophy — which we all can appreciate. Tsarion’s technique brings a breath of fresh air to difficult rhetoric, and this is what I needed for this video. 

Tsarion explains philosophically WHY the religion is shaped as it is, not just how it has been used to arrest the psyche. This idea instigates liberation because it encourages you to doubt. I like to think of this kind of dialog as catharsis via the intellect. 

Understand, during Tsarion’s cameos, he speaks of ancient cataclysms (Younger Dryas for example) and how the psyche of humanity has been traumatized by circumnavigational events that greatly harmed the planet and all creatures living upon it. We are epigenetically affected beings, so our history influences and sets the stage for our experience. We have been marred with forgotten terror throughout our ancestry, and this has been a contributor to our demise. It was cataclysmic events which pounded humanity over time that eventually opened the human mind to a sadistic predation. 

The psychic devices designed by the Cabal and used against humanity over millennia have been hidden beneath politics, religion, science, media, and conducted in such a way to destroy the culture. This makes us easy prey psychologically, and it is from this tendency to fear that we must heal.

To that end, it is my attempt in this video to elucidate the perniciousness of the Cabal, and how they have used hierarchical patriarchies, oppressive governments, caste societies, rigged religions, unarguable science, and instructed ignorance to turn us against ourselves, one another, and Nature.

I hope you can grasp the underlying thread in this video rather than dismiss the points that don’t fit your narrative. Some you will appreciate this, some will not, but if you consider it as a whole rather than a sum of parts, you will see the deeper pattern I am pointing towards. 

Hope you enjoy this. It was fun to make as I learned a lot sorting through literally hours of Tsarion footage to find the opener and closer. 

Cheers-

snippet.title: Human Origin Theory, Part 2
snippet.description:
Today, to begin our venture into heretical origin theory, we have a 5 minute introduction by Dr. Campbell regarding the four functions of mythology. Recognizing the pedagogical, sociological, cosmological, and metaphysical layers of awareness is critical, in my opinion, to awaken past any religious or scientific geometry. 

One of the key instruments of any instructor is using sharp spear which also contains a healing balm on the point. Meaning, a sharp spear of truth will penetrate the meat of mind, but a healing balm must be on the tip so the wound truth leaves can mend itself appropriately. In this idea then, I have included a summery of Dr. Campbell’s work as a healing balm to salve the heretical revelations I present in this movie. The idea is to encourage identity not through a religious notion, but through a basic understanding of the human condition. 

Our perception of Source, however you see or imagine the That which is no that, changes as we experience life and gather wisdom over time. The only logical approach to a deeper understanding of Source then, is to embrace motifs which appropriately align with and are congruent to experienced reality. Science, technology, the internet, experience, space, alternate history, all of these are rendering a world that does not fit into a 2000 year old Bedouin spiritual narrative nor the abomination called evolution, so we must expand our minds past these short sighted, irrelevant, developmentally stagnating assumptions.

The universe, our awareness, the collective conscious, is not going to wait for anyone. Those that refuse to adapt and change their mind will become lost and irrelevant to society while selfishly holding planetary vibration to a lower potential and frustrating the efforts of those who were courageous enough to abandon ideological complacency.

We are in a time of great psychological expansion, and this includes our spiritual cognizance. So this movie is attempting two monumental tasks: 1) encourage self dialog regarding an alternate human origin, and 2) attempt to provide a bridge of understanding that embraces alternate human origin with the actual human condition: love and compassion.

snippet.title: Human Origin Theory, Part 1
snippet.description:
While I wait for the editor to finish with my book, I’m taking a moment to open the door of human origin, aliens, and alternate human history. Human origin and aliens were not in the scope of my book because it’s central theme was Christianity’s psychology and sociology, not history or biology. So this allows us to cover some unique territory before I deep dive into my book and its promotion. The main thrust behind this video is Pierre Sabak, who finally connected some dots for me that long held my perception in check. 

This video is only part one and simply begins a heretical dialog about human origin theory, not claim absolute facts regarding it. We don’t have enough information yet to know for certain the facts, but we are getting closer each month. The Vatican archives will eventually be made public. In this video, Pierre begins an alternate discourse regarding some statements in the Bible as well as —my favorite— practical and matter of fact connections that push all our established human origin theories of evolution and creationism right through the meat grinder. 

Gird your loins fellow sojourner! The disclosure that is coming will not be receivable or recognizable to the fearful, sure, or dependent. Learn to doubt what you assume to know. We all must fearlessly walk into a world none of us has experienced…a space that contains facts which do not align to our preconditioned notions.

snippet.title: According a Beautiful Monster
snippet.description: Today we consider the idea of according with Nature rather than seeing It as a conflict or something to forgive. Living in and accepting Nature as it is can be difficult, because Nature is monstrously powerful and merciless. Nature will relentlessly deliver consequence, and this can seem sadistic if not viewed from a higher consciousness perspective. This video then, is to help ground the observer in awareness, so Nature is no longer a task to master, a race to win, or enterprise to subdue, but a reality to plunge.

snippet.title: Faulty Origins, Tainted Perspectives
snippet.description:
So today we begin scrutinizing the only two western human origin theories. These are pre-ordained, pre-packaged, indoctrinated ways of taking apart the world and ourselves. The first is Creationism and the second Evolutionism. 

These two theories originated from extremely small, “educated”, elitist groups that have controlled thoughts about the world and our origin since before the Sumerians. The implications of this on human understanding cannot be over emphasized. We are still caught up and bound to these assumptions in the same way many are caught up with the idea aliens don’t exist. By having these questions already figured and answered for you as a child, the thought never occurs to question them. They are subsumed as reality like a vitamin is absorbed and becomes flesh. Don’t question, absorb.

The Catholic Church, a corrupt re-costuming of the pedophilic Roman Empire bestowed to us Creationism. Science, an emotionless endeavor attempting to map the universe without any spiritual component, foisted Evolution upon us during the 19th century. These theories frustrate potential because every human must begin their ontological sojourn from short sighted theories that do not account for our potential, are riddled with contradiction, and are developmentally devastating. I mean, for starters the Bible was written under geocentric assumption, and science is basically an unapologetic atheistic endeavor which actually works to dismiss human value. It reminds me of a typical election: those in power offer only their two options, and neither one is palatable. But everyone has to one choose anyway. 

So here we are with western origin theories and everyone has to fall into one of the two options and make sense of everything from that, or they are dismissed as eccentric and quickly anathematized.

Like it or not, the origin you buy into determines life vector. Taint the beginning, and all that follows is skewed. It’s like looking through a telescope, just a fraction of a millimeter off, and entire galaxies are missed. Such is our plight with these bad theories. 

Ask yourself, if we are just glorified slime mold from nothing for no reason (the big bang), or eternally subject to 4th century spiritual hierarchy models based on psychological control mechanisms, how far can we progress as individuals and as a culture? The question answers itself because the contradictions are so blatant and obvious. 

If we are ever going to self identify as individuals we must have a fundamental understanding of ourselves. That begins with knowing our origin in a way that does not demand obedience but inspires appropriate action through appreciation. A way of understanding so fearless, it does not require submitting to a group, but in fact encourages individuation. 

This video is a shot over the bow of the culturally accepted human origin narratives. It is simply a thought tool to open new doors of thought as we all unlearn during the Great Awakening.

snippet.title: Hunters of Spirit
snippet.description:
Many people have a vested interest in being sick or weak because there is nothing more frightening than being completely well, because then you have to take responsibility for your life, and the world around you. 

In this video, Terence McKenna takes us on a 15 minute journey into shamanism, and suggests through shamanistic techniques how we each can become exemplars of humanity. This is done by utilizing Nature's biological technology, namely plants, to heal the indoctrinated mind.

The concern of this video, ayahuasca, is not to claim it as a panacea, rather as a medicinal wrecking ball known to have cured everything from heroin addiction, to Parkinson's disease, to depression, to deep seeded emotional trauma and behavioral dysfunctions like obsessive compulsive disorders and seizures. Ayahuasca cleans the blood, liver, and gall bladder. It cleanses the emotional field by allowing us to process our old traumas, and liberate ourselves.

snippet.title: The Quaking Mess

Enjoy!

snippet.title: The science and biology behind cannabis and addiction
snippet.description:
This video explains how cannabis works directly with the Autonomic Nervous System (ANS) and the endocannabinoid system to heal the body. The ANS is central to addiction, and so this video also explains how cannabis effectively treats physiological addiction to drugs like: alcohol, tobacco, caffeine, opioids, accelerants, depressants--the banes of modern society. Basically, the why's and how's of cannabis are rendered though science in a way anyone can understand and appreciate in this 14 min video. 
Peace -
